This repository contains deployment configuration (Docker, Kubernetes) for
running the Argo CD Model Context Protocol server.

The MCP server itself is the npm package `argocd-mcp`, developed by the Argo
Project and distributed under the Apache License 2.0.

  Homepage:  https://github.com/argoproj-labs/mcp-for-argocd
  npm:       https://www.npmjs.com/package/argocd-mcp

This repo does not redistribute the server source code; at runtime the
container installs `argocd-mcp` from npm per the Dockerfile.
